{
  "stem": "27509.9",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I published my book, my autobiography, which had a very good reception-- and you have seen one of the critiques-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Doctor Foster, who read my manuscript on his own-- on his own initiative talked to Professor [NON-ENGLISH], who was then a professor of economic-- the professor, the professor of economic history at Melbourne University, who, in turn, invited me to come and see him and suggested that I should write the history of the knitting industry in Victoria, as a doctoral thesis.",
      "word_count": 87
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- and I say that with the benefit of hindsight-- a little bit [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] too easy in saying yes, because that-- I wanted to write a doctoral thesis.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I wanted to continue in the field in which I have written my-- my-- the honors and my master's.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I want to continue in this field, because that was the field which touched on the very essence of the relations between world Jew and the new State of Israel, which are so profound and so sensitive, and becoming more sensitive with time.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for that, I would have had to go and interview people all over the world, and the personalities in America, and in Israel, and so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's what I wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it did not-- it did not turn out this way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was an opportunity for me to-- to study at [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We went to Boston, and my wife had one look at it, at the snow there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she said, you can stay here as long as you like.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm going back to Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was the end of that idea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, I spent one and a half hours-- one half-- beg your pardon.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
